od that throws an exception?','Yes','No','Only if types match','Only for checked exceptions','A'),(305,'Polymorphism','Method overloading happens in which class?','Parent only','Child only','Same class or within hierarchy','Only interfaces','C'),(306,'Polymorphism','Method overriding occurs between ______ classes.','Sibling','The same','Superclass and Subclass','Independent','C'),(307,'Polymorphism','In overriding, the method signature must be ______?','Different','Same','Only name same','Only return type same','B'),(308,'Polymorphism','What is Dynamic Method Dispatch?','A call to overridden method resolved at runtime','A call to overloaded method at runtime','A way to hide data','A way to cast objects','A'),(309,'Polymorphism','Can a static method be overridden?','Yes','No','Only if it is public','Only in Java 8','B'),(310,'Polymorphism','Redefining a parent static method in a child is called?','Overriding','Method Hiding','Overloading','Abstraction','B'),(311,'Polymorphism','Can a final method be overridden?','Yes','No','Only if it is protected','Only in abstract classes','B'),(312,'Polymorphism','Can a private method be overridden?','Yes','No','Only if in the same package','Only if protected','B'),(313,'Polymorphism','What is Covariant Return Type?','Subclass method returning a subtype of parent return type','Subclass method returning a different primitive type','Parent method returning a child type','None','A'),(314,'Polymorphism','Can the access modifier be more restrictive in the overriding method?','Yes','No','Only for protected','Only for static','B'),(315,'Polymorphism','Which annotation is used to verify method overriding?','@Overload','@Inherit','@Override','@Polymorphic','C'),(316,'Polymorphism','If a parent method throws a checked exception, can the child throw a broader one?','Yes','No','Only if it is static','Only if it is final','B'),(317,'Polymorphism','Can we override a method to throw a narrower checked exception?','Yes','No','Only for runtime exc