 thrown if Downcasting is invalid at runtime?','NullPointerException','ArithmeticException','ClassCastException','RuntimeException','C'),(331,'Polymorphism','Which operator helps prevent ClassCastException?','typeof','instanceof','check','is','B'),(332,'Polymorphism','What does (new Dog() instanceof Animal) return if Dog extends Animal?','true','false','Compile error','null','A'),(333,'Polymorphism','Can you downcast a parent reference to a child type if it actually holds a parent object?','Yes','No (ClassCastException)','Only if static','Only if final','B'),(334,'Polymorphism','Upcasting allows access to ______?','Only child specific methods','Only parent methods','Both parent and child methods','Neither','B'),(335,'Polymorphism','Downcasting is used to access ______?','Parent methods','Child specific methods','Private variables','Static methods','B'),(336,'Polymorphism','If A is parent of B, is \"B b = (B) new A();\" valid?','Compiles, but fails at runtime','Compile error','Always valid','Only if B is abstract','A'),(337,'Polymorphism','instanceof returns true for null?','Yes','No','Only for Object class','Only in Java 17+','B'),(338,'Polymorphism','Reference type determines which methods are ______?','Visible','Executed','Private','Static','A'),(339,'Polymorphism','Object type determines which methods are ______?','Visible','Executed at runtime','Private','Final','B'),(340,'Polymorphism','Can we upcast an object to an interface it implements?','Yes','No','Only for abstract classes','Only for final classes','A'),(341,'Polymorphism','Are variables polymorphic in Java?','Yes','No (they use static binding)','Only static variables','Only final variables','B'),(342,'Polymorphism','Data member overriding is possible?','Yes','No','Only in Java 8','Only for protected members','B'),(343,'Polymorphism','If Child extends Parent and both have a variable \"x\", which \"x\" is accessed via Parent ref?','Parent\'s x','Child\'s x','Both','Compilation error','A'),(344,'Polymorphis